#: ../../first-time-setup.rst:2
msgid "First time setup"
msgstr "Mise en place initiale"

#: ../../first-time-setup.rst:4
msgid ""
"Once the module is installed, you need to configure the system to execute the "
"``cronical`` script periodically. This script will check if actions need to be "
"executed and execute them."
msgstr ""
"Une fois le module installé, vous devez configurer le système pour qu'il "
"exécute le script ``cronical`` périodiquement. Ce script vérifiera si des "
"actions ont besoin d'être exécutés et les exécutera."

#: ../../first-time-setup.rst:8
msgid "There are different ways to do that. We will explain the most common ones."
msgstr ""
"Il y a plusieurs façons de faire ça. Nous allons expliquer les plus communes."

#: ../../first-time-setup.rst:10
msgid ""
"Note that in the following examples we configure the system to run the "
"``cronical`` script every minute. It is not required to do so.  For instance "
"you can run it every hour and it will execute all actions that should have been "
"executed in the past hour. So adjust according to your needs."
